data.description: Welcome home to this stunning townhome located in the gated community of Northside Commons. You will love the open floorplan featuring hardwood floors throughout the first floor and beautiful natural light. The family room opens to a flawless kitchen with granite countertops, beautiful stained cabinets, and a large island. The homeowner's retreat boasts an oversized primary bedroom, large walk-in closet, and a spacious ensuite bathroom. The two secondary bedrooms provide all the space you've been looking for. The 2-car garage and long driveway provide plenty of parking space for you and your guests. This neighborhood oasis features a swimming pool, tennis courts and a clubhouse. Ideally located just minutes from downtown Winder. This could be the one you've been waiting for!
